  <prompt>
    Add unit tests for the 3 split hooks (`useBriefingNotifications`, `useBriefingPreferences`, `useBriefingActions`) — independent test fixtures, no shared state. Add a smoke test that mounts `DailyBriefingApp` with mocked `Xrm` + asserts the BFF `/narrate` call fires with a non-empty payload. Closes the NFR-05 test gap.
  </prompt>

  <role>SPAARKE platform developer. Expert in React Testing Library + Vitest/Jest + mocking `Xrm.WebApi`.</role>

  <goal>Three independent hook tests + one smoke test exist and pass. Test coverage for the new package is measurable and reported.</goal>

  <context>
    <background>
      Per NFR-05: new shared package ships with unit tests for the 3 split hooks + smoke test mounting `DailyBriefingApp` with mocked Xrm. Fills the test gap identified in the audit.
