  <steps>
    <step order="1">Set up test infrastructure in new package (mirror `@spaarke/events-components/test/` config).</step>
    <step order="2">Write `useBriefingNotifications.test.ts` — mock `webApi`, assert `channels`, `totalUnreadCount`, `refetch` behave per FR-06 contract.</step>
    <step order="3">Write `useBriefingPreferences.test.ts` — mock `webApi`, assert `preferences`, `updatePreferences`, loading + error states.</step>
    <step order="4">Write `useBriefingActions.test.ts` — assert `markAsRead`, `markAllAsRead`, `dismissAll`, `refresh`.</step>
    <step order="5">Write `DailyBriefingApp.smoke.test.tsx` — render with mocked `Xrm`, mocked `authenticatedFetch`; assert `/narrate` fetch fires with non-empty payload; assert at least one channel renders.</step>
    <step order="6">Run `npm test` in new package; all green.</step>
    <step order="7">Record coverage report in `notes/` for project tracking.</step>
    <step order="8">Update TASK-INDEX.md: change task 019 status from 🔲 to ✅.</step>
  </steps>

